TIER 3 — Polish & replayability
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
League Customization — expansion teams, relocation, custom team names beyond
  the Team Editor. Relocation wizard, stadium naming, fan base effects.

In-Game Narrative / Play-by-Play — text play-by-play during simulation.
  Stats-only output today limits immersion significantly.

Preset Dynasty Templates — fictional franchise starter kits selectable at new
  dynasty creation. Each template ships as a pre-built CSV: roster of fictional
  players, team ratings, historical records, and league configuration. Examples:
  "Rebuild Mode" (60–70 OVR roster, tight cap), "Contender Window" (stacked but
  aging), "Dynasty Peak" (league powerhouse, high expectations). Lowers barrier
  to entry and provides structured challenge modes.

================================================================================
GAMEPLAY DEPTH — OOTP-Tier Features
================================================================================
Features that would bring the game to a competitive level with top sports sims.

NARRATIVE & STAKES
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Team Chemistry / Locker Room System — team-level morale modifier on top of
  individual player morale. Winning streaks boost it, losing streaks tank it,
  star players leaving damages it. Affects sim ratings for the entire roster.

Player Personality Archetypes — leadership, work ethic, and coachability
  ratings per player beyond dev trait. Affects development speed, locker room
  health, and contract negotiation behavior.

ROSTER / PLAYER MANAGEMENT
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Injury History / Injury-Prone Trait — track career injury history per player.
  Players with repeated injuries accumulate an injury-prone flag that increases
  in-game injury probability and lowers market value.

Scouting Department — hire scouts with regional specialties that improve draft
  prospect accuracy over time. Builds directly on the existing combine
  measurables and in-season scouting budget system.

SIMULATION & SCHEDULE
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Multi-Season Batch Simulation — "Sim N seasons" with a progress bar. Critical
  for dynasty feel — users should be able to fast-forward through rebuilds.

LEAGUE & FINANCIALS
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Financial System Beyond Cap — market size per team affecting revenue, stadium
  attendance, and owner budget. Large market vs. small market affecting cap
  floor and FA appeal.

